### Global Variables
@host = http://localhost:8000

### 1. 학년도 생성 (관리자)
POST {{host}}/schedule/years
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}

{
  "year": 2026,
  "semester": 1,
  "startDate": "2026-03-02",
  "endDate": "2026-06-20"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("academic_year_id", response.body.data);
%}

### 2. 과목 생성 (관리자)
POST {{host}}/subjects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}

{
  "name": "고급수학"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("subject_id", response.body.data);
%}

### 3. 과목 목록 조회
GET {{host}}/subjects
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{student_access_token}}

### 4. 학사 일정 등록 (관리자)
POST {{host}}/schedule/events
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}

{
  "academicYearId": {{academic_year_id}},
  "scheduleDate": "2026-04-15",
  "scheduleType": "EXAM",
  "content": "1학기 중간고사",
  "targetGrade": 0
}

> {%
  client.global.set("schedule_id", response.body.data);
%}

### 5. 학사 일정 수정 (관리자)
PUT {{host}}/schedule/events/{{schedule_id}}
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}

{
  "academicYearId": {{academic_year_id}},
  "scheduleDate": "2026-04-16",
  "scheduleType": "EXAM",
  "content": "1학기 중간고사 (일정 변경)",
  "targetGrade": 0
}

### 6. 월간 일정 조회
GET {{host}}/schedule/events/monthly?year=2026&month=4
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer {{student_access_token}}

### 7. 학사 일정 삭제 (관리자)
DELETE {{host}}/schedule/events/{{schedule_id}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_access_token}}
